From tonight onward,
I will sleep in the living room.

13
00:01:26,667 --> 00:01:29,167
I'm the one who lodges here
Sleeping on the Sofa is fine for me.

14
00:01:29,267 --> 00:01:32,067
No, Shyuuhei is the last one to go to bed.

15
00:01:32,167 --> 00:01:34,233
