Misaki, you sleep in the bedroom.

18
00:01:44,833 --> 00:01:46,867
Shyuuhei, you go sleep in the other room.

19
00:01:49,933 --> 00:01:51,200
I got it.

20
00:01:51,967 --> 00:01:53,833
Shyuuhie, is one piece of bread enough?

21
00:01:53,933 --> 00:01:55,100
Mhm.

22
