He would kiss me like that without realizing it.

23
00:02:16,867 --> 00:02:20,467
Does this mean...
he would kiss like this with Yuuki?

24
00:02:34,533 --> 00:02:36,367
- This is good.
- Is it so?

25
00:02:36,467 --> 00:02:37,567
Good morning.

